data.title: Hiten & Gauri are now GODPARENTS to actress Amita Chandekar's baby girl!
meta_keywords: Kyunki Saas Bhi Kabhi Bahu Thi
data.meta_description: Hiten & Gauri are now GODPARENTS to actress Amita Chandekar's baby girl!
data.text:
Hiten Tejwani and Gauri Pradhan are one of the most loved couples of Indian Television. The TV couple, who has worked with each other in shows like 'Kutumb', 'Kyunki Saas Bhi Kabhi Bahu Thi', are already parents to 8-year-old twins Katya and Neevan. Hiten and Gauri have now turned godparents to TV actress Amita Chandekar's baby girl 'Zya'. Hiten-Gauri got married in 2007 (Photo: Web) Currently seen in 'Colors' show 'Tu Aashiqui', TV actress Gauri shared the great news on her social media account. She posted a picture with Zya in her arms along with hubby Hiten and kids. The pictures has been captioned as, "Thank you zya for choosing us to be your god parents!!love you❤️❤️❤️#zya’s baptism#sanjose #excitement #godparents #goddaughter" Karan Patel's ex-girlfriend Amita Chandekar, who tied the knot with Ritesh Tiwari in 2010, shared pictures from the name giving ceremony on her Instagram account. Check out the pictures here: Hiten Tejwani-Gauri's LIP-LOCK on their 14th WEDDING ANNIVERSARY will make you fall in love! Hiten Tejwani in a SNOW-LAND with wife Gauri and their ROMANTIC PICS will make you go green with envy! For the uninitiated, baptism is performed on young children and is accompanied by name-giving. Amita with Karan Patel in 'Nach Baliye (Photo: Web) Speaking about Amita, she has been a part of various popular 'Balaji' shows 'Kyunki Saas Bhi Kabhi Thi', 'Kutumb', 'Kkutumb' among others. She also participated in 'Nach Baliye 3' with ex beau Karan Patel. She is now happily married to Ritesh and is settled in California. Heartiest congratulations to them!
